(; External Disagreement Test Battery v1 — 2026-04-29)(; Tests: inject conflicting external evidence, measure Q_AMBIGUOUS, oscillation, cascade containment)(; Component 1: Same-term opposing-frequency injector)(= (internal-belief robin-flies) (stv 0.95 0.85))(= (external-belief robin-flies) (stv 0.15 0.70))(= (disagreement-score $term) (let* (((stv $f1 $c1) (internal-belief $term)) ((stv $f2 $c2) (external-belief $term))) (* (abs (- $f1 $f2)) (min $c1 $c2))))(; Component 2: Source-trust confidence scaling)(= (source-trust self-derived) 0.9)(= (source-trust web-search) 0.7)(= (source-trust user-asserted) 0.4)(= (source-trust unknown) 0.1)(= (effective-conf $raw_c $source) (* $raw_c (source-trust $source)))(; Component 3: Q_AMBIGUOUS production — expect revised midrange freq)(; Component 4: Oscillation detector — flag if >2 consecutive flips)(= (oscillation-flag $term $flip_count) (> $flip_count 2))(; Component 5: Evidence-seeking trigger on Q_AMBIGUOUS)(= (seek-evidence $term) (oscillation-flag $term 0))